contentrichtext.text: '''[[Shetland]]''' is an archipelago in Scotland. It may also refer to: *[[South Shetland Islands]], a group of islands in the South Atlantic *[[Short Shetland]], a 1940s British flying boat *[[Shetland animal breeds]], including: **[[Shetland Cattle]] **[[Shetland Pony]] **[[Shetland (sheep)]] **[[Shetland Sheepdog]] **[[Shetland Goose]] *''[[Shetland (TV series)|Shetland]]'', a [[Crime film#In television|crime drama]] television series airing on the [[BBC]], set in the Shetland Islands. {{disambig}}
